_:Nf6f18b1adc34425da80ec97cb6bc73bf <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Luke Pollard was appointed Minister of State in the Ministry of Defence on 6 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>He was previously Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State in the Ministry of Defence from 9 July 2024 to 6 September 2025. He was elected as the MP for Plymouth Sutton and Devonport in July 2024.</p>\n" .
